        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1212",
        "content": "But she declared that he had given them more fun than if he had not come over, and the molasses had cooled and they had had a regular candy pull.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
